	<h1 class="title">外卖这么难吃，却还有好多人抱有希望 | 好奇心研究所</h1>
	<div class="author-date clearfix">					
			<div class="author clearfix">
					<span class="avatar x25 circle">
						<img src="/system/users/faces/1288/small/1288.gif?1404690740" alt="">
					</span>
				<span class="name">胡昱 </span>
			</div>
		<span class="date smart-date" data-originDate="2015-06-23 15:48:49 +0800"></span>
	</div>
	<div class="banner">
			<img src="/system/articles/articleshows/11128/medium/11128.jpg?1436642452" alt="" />			
	</div>
	<!-- 传入参数：obj(aritcle, paper, card, mob) -->


<div class="com-share" data-id="11128" data-title="《外卖这么难吃，却还有好多人抱有希望 | 好奇心研究所》，来自@好奇心日报" data-pic="http://www.qdaily.com/system/articles/articleshows/11128/medium/11128.jpg?1436642452" data-url="http://www.qdaily.com/mobile/articles/11128" data-weiboAppkey="2462590045">
